'''鲟科'''（Acipenseridae）是[[鲟形目|鲟形目]]下的一個科，其下有4屬、27种魚類，其中4种可能已經滅絕<ref name="IUCN">{{cite web | url=http://www.iucn.org/?4928/Sturgeon-more-critically-endangered-than-any-other-group-of-species | title=Sturgeon More Critically Endangered Than Any Other Group of Species | publisher=International Union for Conservation of Nature | work=International News Release | date=March 18, 2010 | accessdate=September 19, 2015 | author1=Chadwick, Niki | author2=Drzewinski, Pia | author3=Hurt, Leigh Ann | archive-date=2016-04-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420115828/http://www.iucn.org/?4928%2FSturgeon-more-critically-endangered-than-any-other-group-of-species | dead-url=no }}</ref>。鱘魚生活在[[海洋|海洋]]和大的[[河流|河流]]、[[湖泊|湖泊]]中，体长可達數米。其化石記錄可追溯到2.45至2.08億年前的[[三疊紀|三疊紀]]時期<ref>Birstein, V.J., R. Hanner, and R. DeSalle. 1997. Phylogeny of the Acipenseriformes: cytogenic and molecular approaches. Environmental Biology of Fishes 48: 127-155.</ref>。[[匙吻鲟|匙吻鲟]]和[[白鱘|白鱘]]雖然與鱘科魚類很像，但實際屬於不同的科。不過所有的這些鱘魚因爲化石記錄久遠，都被稱為[[活化石|活化石]]<ref name=USFWS>{{cite web|title=Atlantic Sturgeon|url=http://www.fws.gov/chesapeakebay/sturgeon.html|publisher=U.S. Fish & Wildlife Service|author=Chesapeake Bay Field Office|accessdate=June 10, 2014|archive-date=2019-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190615220637/https://www.fws.gov/chesapeakebay/sturgeon.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Lake sturgeon|url=http://www.dnr.state.mn.us/rsg/profile.html?action=elementDetail&selectedElement=AFCAA01020|publisher=Minnesota Dept. of Natural Resources|accessdate=June 10, 2014|archive-date=2021-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210508131346/https://www.dnr.state.mn.us/rsg/profile.html?action=elementDetail&selectedElement=AFCAA01020|dead-url=no}}</ref>。鱘生活在歐亞大陸和北美洲的熱帶、溫帶及亞寒帶水域中<ref name=WashingtonEdu>{{cite web|url=http://courses.washington.edu/fish311/FISH%20311%20files/08-Primitive%20bony.pdf|publisher=University of Washington|title=Biology of Fishes (chapter: Biodiversity II: Primitive Bony Fishes and The Rise of Modern Teleosts)|accessdate=May 30, 2014|archive-date=2014-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140601003623/http://courses.washington.edu/fish311/FISH%20311%20files/08-Primitive%20bony.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

鲟科的鱼口前有四须和口排长一横列，生活在海中的一般春季向大江河中洄游产卵。性成熟较迟，因为被人类捕获的多，面临绝种的危险，现在许多国家都加以保护。

==生命週期==
鱘科的魚類都很長壽，一般能活50到60年，15到20歲時才開始產卵。它們並非每年都產卵，產卵需要滿足特定的環境要求，比如適當的春季[[光周期|光周期]]、乾淨的水質和碎石河床。一條鱘魚一次能產下10萬至300萬枚卵，但並非所有卵都會受精。卵附著於河床，在8至15日後孵化<ref name="BCME">{{cite web | url=http://www.env.gov.bc.ca/wld/fishhabitats/sturgeon/ | publisher=British Columbia Ministry of Environment, Ecosystems Branch | title=Fish & Habitats– White Sturgeon (Acipenser transmontanus) in British Columbia | accessdate=October 28, 2015 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180522054726/http://www.env.gov.bc.ca/wld/fishhabitats/sturgeon/ | archive-date=2018-05-22 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=HSBC>{{cite web| url=http://hsbc.frasersturgeon.com/rhspsec/Lesson1/Articles/Article1.pdf| title=Life Cycle of the White Sturgeon| publisher=Fraser River Conservation Society| work=HSBC Fraser River Sturgeon Education Program| accessdate=October 28, 2015| archive-date=2021-01-24| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124052458/https://hsbc.frasersturgeon.com/rhspsec/Lesson1/Articles/Article1.pdf| dead-url=no}}</ref>。它們順著河流進入海洋，在那裡度過一年。一年後體長可達{{convert|18|-|20|cm|in}}，並返回河流中。<ref name="govinfo 1976">{{cite web | title=Investigations of anadromous fishes of the Neuse River, North Carolina | website=govinfo | date=May 1, 1976 | url=https://www.govinfo.gov/content/pkg/CZIC-ql628-n8-h3-1980/html/CZIC-ql628-n8-h3-1980.htm | access-date=April 22, 2019 | archive-date=2021-02-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204032429/https://www.govinfo.gov/content/pkg/CZIC-ql628-n8-h3-1980/html/CZIC-ql628-n8-h3-1980.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>

==下级分类==
鲟科有4属23种。中国有2属。包括以下属：<ref>{{cite web |title=Acipenseridae |url=https://www.gbif.org/species/2947 |website=GBIF}}</ref>
* [[鲟属|鲟属]] ''Acipenser'' Linnaeus, 1758
* [[鳇属|鳇属]] ''Huso'' Brandt & Ratzeburg, 1833
* [[扁鲟属|扁鲟属]] ''Priscosturion'' Grande & Hilton, 2009
* ''Propenser'' Applegate, 1970
* [[原鲴鲟属|原鲴鲟属]] ''Protoscaphirhynchus'' Wilimovsky, 1956
* ''Psammorhynchus'' Grande & Hilton, 2006
* [[拟铲鲟属|拟铲鲟属]] ''Pseudoscaphirhynchus'' Nikolskii, 1900
* ''Rhineastes''
* [[铲鲟属|铲鲟属]] ''Scaphirhynchus'' Heckel, 1836
* ''Sturio'' Müller, 1836

